<br>
&quot;I don't know what's on the other side.&quot; Riverdane said to his four companions. &quot;And I don't know if it will acknowledge me as a god. Nor if it did if it would matter.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;So basically...&quot; Whizbang began.<br>
<br>
