<br>
&quot;I thought you stored it all in that huge forehead of yours.&quot; the ogre voice cut in.<br>
<br>
&quot;Kiss my ass, Pron.&quot; Tremas said back. &quot;Alright, I'll get Ake this time. But give me a little downtime too, not like we doing this with a chanter.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Lovely,&quot; Riverdane said. &quot;Promethian Order is here.&quot;<br>
<br>
