<br>
Promethian Order. One of the oldest and affluent military guilds of Norrath. Acceptance into the ranks of Promethian Order was akin to an adventurer coming of age. Its members had seen many things other guilds only dream of doing. And there were two of the members, sitting among a pile of corpses of the denizens of Fear. Dead scarelings, phoboplasms, nightmares, turmoil toads littered the camp site. And in the middle, Pron, a huge ogre warlord in full battle gear, and Aamedor, one of Promethian Order's high priests and former member of River's guild. Tremas was nowhere to be seen.<br>
<br>
Aamedor saw them first. &quot;Hey, River.&quot; he said with a smile. &quot;And Whiz, Pedi. What brings you here? Alliance coming up?&quot;<br>
<br>
